you have all these streaming

00:27:34.190 --> 00:27:34.991 align:middle line:90%
videos--

00:27:34.991 --> 00:27:36.281 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Like this network, yes.

00:27:36.281 --> 00:27:37.640 align:middle line:90%
