Leo, or an Aries--

00:28:33.297 --> 00:28:34.880 align:middle line:84%
those are all the
fire signs-- they're

00:28:34.880 --> 00:28:36.530 align:middle line:90%
going to benefit from this.

00:28:36.530 --> 00:28:41.180 align:middle line:84%
But then in December, Jupiter
will move into Capricorn,

00:28:41.180 --> 00:28:44.810 align:middle line:84%
and then the Earth signs
will get their turn.

00:28:44.810 --> 00:28:47.960 align:middle line:84%
Capricorn, Virgo, and
Taurus, but also the water

00:28:47.960 --> 00:28:50.960 align:middle line:84%
signs Pisces, and
Cancer, and Scorpio.

00:28:50.960 --> 00:28:54.120 align:middle line:84%
So the universe is an
equal opportunity employer,

00:28:54.120 --> 00:28:54.920 align:middle line:90%
so to speak.

00:28:54.920 --> 00:28:57.045 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So you should look
at the year ahead as one

00:28:57.045 --> 00:28:57.980 align:middle line:90%
with gifts and luck.

00:28:57.980 --> 00:28:59.030 align:middle line:90%
>>MILLER: Oh, absolutely.

