I talk a lot about that.

00:29:00.740 --> 00:29:03.800 align:middle line:84%
But also, Saturn is
the great teacher.

00:29:03.800 --> 00:29:07.797 align:middle line:84%
So he challenges us,
and we have to learn.

00:29:07.797 --> 00:29:08.630 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's life.

00:29:08.630 --> 00:29:11.330 align:middle line:84%
