so we can learn and grow.

00:29:11.330 --> 00:29:12.650 align:middle line:90%
>>MILLER: Yeah.

00:29:12.650 --> 00:29:17.570 align:middle line:84%
I think people make too
much of the difficulties.

00:29:17.570 --> 00:29:20.270 align:middle line:90%
And you can face it.

